-- Shares of Banco do Brasil rise on earnings beat
-- By Asher Levine
-- Thu Aug 14, 2014 09:08AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, Aug 14 (Reuters) - Shares of Brazilian state-run lender Banco do Brasil SA <BBAS3.SA> climbed on Thursday after the company reported better-than-expected recurring net income for the second quarter. [ID:nL2N0QK0G6]

